latestIgtvVideos.title: Simple Spider Gel Manicure
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi guys...🖐 today I'm trying something new....as in new for me. I have been watching the spider gel named stringy gel making rounds in the nail world. So thought of giving it a try....🤔
It is quite easy to use once you get the hang of it. the more you dip in the pot the thicker the string will be. It has to be cured for a minute n cleaned with rubbing alcohol to remove sticky layer. To remove any excess just use normal remover before curing....😊
Products used
Spider Gel: @ursugar_official UR-01 which is available at @nailart_nailsfiesta. 
Base color: @lovecolorbar 'Love Bug' 
Cuticle cover: @go.diva.nail cuticle cover
This is my first time using it....that's why kept it really simple. But as I'll get more comfi with it I make more designs....😊
Hope y'all like it.....enjoy...😘
#igtv #spidergel #ursugar #nailfiesta #lovecolorbar
